title: SPLEEF RULES
author: itzliam3
pages:
#- ***********************H-DOME Spleef Rules
***********************
#- 1. No placing of blocks from players or spectators when a match in is play. If a block is placed the offending player loses the match. If a spectator interferes a rematch is called. 

2. Potions are not allowed. 
#- 3. Players are not allowed to hit eachother. Three hits cause the offending player to lose the match. 

4. Beginning before the announcer announces "GO" results in a restart. 

5. No foreign objects
#- 6. Leaving the playing area results in a lost match.   

7. If a player punches a another player off the playing area the offending player loses the match, even if the hit was not on purpose. 
#- 